", "start": 271.845, "end": 272.345}, {"text": "And this is exactly the same situation.", "start": 274.87, "end": 277.19}, {"text": "Now now Trump is saying, I will not be dying for Ukraine.", "start": 277.19, "end": 282.425}, {"text": "Okay.", "start": 282.425, "end": 282.925}, {"text": "If they will give us all the resources, maybe I will consider this.", "start": 283.225, "end": 288.425}], "num_words": 34, "start": 271.845, "end": 288.425}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Right?", "start": 288.425, "end": 288.925}, {"text": "And this is just colonialistic colonialistic policy.", "start": 289.05, "end": 299.01495}, {"text": "Right?", "start": 299.01495, "end": 299.49493}, {"text": "I mean", "start": 299.49493, "end": 300}], "num_words": 11, "start": 288.425, "end": 300}]}}]}, {"alternatives": [{"transcript": "In the whole of South Africa, the big mountains, you can get some snow in the winter, but the top top. But in this place, you can actually get snow. The 1 time I was riding horses, we were going for, we call it an outride, so into the forest and it was cold. And then all of a sudden it starts snowing. So I''m riding horses in South Africa and we have all the snow. I promise you it was the most beautiful thing ever. I loved it. I couldn''t believe that we had this in South Africa. I was very lucky. Not many people get to ride horses in the snow. So this, this was brilliant and in South Africa, of all places. But I will tell you that now, I think sometimes the winters can get very cold, but not for long. And, you know, with the snow, I don''t think it''s been as much as before. So, yeah, things are changing. And our summer has taken very long to get here, but it''s finally here. Only now really are we getting that big heat that we normally see from December already. This is now February, middle of February. So things are going on, and it''s really, really crazy. But I wanted to ask you, things are happening with Ukraine, with Poland, with Trump, all these things. So I