 Ukraine, with Poland, with Trump, all these things. So I heard the other day, Trump had a phone call with Putin, but not with Zelensky.\n\nAnd then he spoke to Zelensky after that. And there is talks of potentially stopping the war. What does Poland think about this? Do you believe that this war can end with the involvement of America like this? What do you think?\n\nDo you believe it? Do you not believe it? Yeah. Good. In the media.\n\nIn the media. Rumors. Yeah. Oh. Yalta.\n\nNo. Oh. 0, okay. Yeah. Yeah.\n\nYeah. Yeah. Yeah. Colonialistic. Colonialistic.\n\nYeah. Yeah.", "paragraphs": [{"sentences": [{"text": "In the whole of South Africa, the big mountains, you can get some snow in the winter, but the top top.", "start": 0.16, "end": 6.1}, {"text": "But in this place, you can actually get snow.", "start": 6.3199997, "end": 9.3}, {"text": "The 1 time I was riding horses, we were going for, we call it an outride, so into the forest and it was cold.", "start": 9.434999, "end": 17.134998}, {"text": "And then all of a sudden it starts snowing.", "start": 17.42, "end": 19.52}, {"text": "So I''m riding horses in South Africa and we have all the snow.", "start": 19.66, "end": 24.08}], "num_words": 76, "start": 0.16, "end": 24.08}, {"sentences": [{"text": "I promise you it was the most beautiful thing ever.", "start": 24.3, "end": 26.295}, {"text": "I loved it.", "start": 26.295, "end": 27.015001}, {"text": "I couldn''t believe that we had this in South Africa.", "start": 27.015001, "end": 30.055}, {"text": "I was very lucky.", "start": 30.055, "end": 30.935001}, {"text": "Not many people get to ride horses in the snow.", "start": 30.935001, "end": 33.595}], "num_words": 37, "start": 24.3, "end": 33.595}, {"sentences": [{"text": "So this, this was brilliant and in South Africa, of all places.", "start": 34.79, "end": 39.13}, {"text": "But I will tell you that now, I think sometimes the winters can get very cold, but not for long.", "start": 39.350002, "end": 46.405003}, 