 socialistic communism, idea, including Poland. And nobody asked us whether we want to be, there or not. This was just, you know, like, I believe it was based on what what whether we whether the US and UK the UK, want war with Russia to, gain Poland, Czech Republic, Czechoslovakia at that time, or not, or maybe\n\nChannel 1: Yeah.\n\nChannel 0: Baltic countries and take it over to and, like, rejoin them to the Western Europe. And I I mean, they they they had clear picture that they they will not be dying for Poland.\n\nChannel 1: Yeah.\n\nChannel 0: Right?\n\nChannel 1: Yeah. Yeah.\n\nChannel 0: And this is exactly the same situation. Now now Trump is saying, I will not be dying for Ukraine. Okay. If they will give us all the resources, maybe I will consider this. Right?\n\nAnd this is just colonialistic\n\nChannel 1: Colonialistic. Colonialistic.\n\nChannel 0: colonialistic policy.\n\nChannel 1: Yeah.\n\nChannel 0: Right?\n\nChannel 1: Yeah.\n\nChannel 0: I mean", "paragraphs": [{"sentences": [{"text": "In the whole of South Africa, the big mountains, you can get some snow in the winter, but the top top.", "start": 0.16, "end": 6.1}, {"text": "But in this place, you can actually get snow.", "start": 6.3199997, "end": 9.3}, {"text": "The 1 time I was riding horses, we were going for, we call it an outride, so into the forest and it was cold.", "start": 9.434999, "end": 17.134998}, {"text": "And then all of a sudden it starts snowing.", "start": 17.42, "end": 19.52}, {"text": "So I''m riding horses in South Africa and we have all the snow.", "start": 19.66, "end": 24.08}], "channel": 1, "num_words": 76, "start": 0.16, "end": 24.08}, {"sentences": [{"text": "I promise you it was the most beautiful thing ever.", "start": 24.3, "end": 26.295}, {"text": "I loved it.", "start": 26.295, "end": 27.015001}, {"text": "I couldn''t believe that we had this in South Africa.", "start": 27.015001, "end": 30.055}, {"text": "I was very lucky.", "start": 30.055, "end": 30.935001}, {"